## 🖨️ Print in Linux

<details>
<summary>Click to expand</summary>

```bash
echo ----> To print in linux
```

### Examples:

```bash
echo "welcome to ss training"
```

Output:

```text
welcome to ss training
```

```bash
echo -e "welcome \nss training"
```

Output:

```text
welcome
ss training
```

